enc_save_binar...ng_constraints(25.10)  enc_save_binar...ng_constraints(25.10)

Name
       enc_save_binary_timing_constraints

Syntax
       enc_save_binary_timing_constraints {true | false}

       Type: Boolean

       Default: true

       If  set  to true, saveDesign will save binary timing constraints by de-
       fault, but only for those used in "active" constraint modes. These  are
       the constraint modes used in set_analysis_view.  The SDC files saved by
       saveDesign  have  the  suffix  ".tcz",  and  are  saved  directly under
       .enc.dat/.

Related Information
              * restoreDesign

              * saveDesign

